# Code owners for security- and policy-sensitive paths. A pull request that
# touches any of these auto-requests the maintainer as a reviewer — and once
# branch protection has "Require review from Code Owners" enabled on master,
# such a PR cannot merge without that review.
#
# This is the safeguard for the license policy: a contributor whose change
# introduces a new license must edit license-policy.json to classify it, and
# that edit forces a deliberate maintainer review.

/license-policy.json   @Jared-Dev
/pnpm-workspace.yaml    @Jared-Dev
/package.json          @Jared-Dev
/LICENSE               @Jared-Dev
/cla/                  @Jared-Dev
/scripts/              @Jared-Dev
/.github/              @Jared-Dev
